_sText:
**bhop_eosin.** This is my second map. The map features a simple theme, and finishes off in a realistic setting . Multi-stage map with increasing difficulty. Should take about 3-4mins to finish on auto.

_The map is possible on scroll (I spent a few hours testing it to make sure), however I'm not sure if it's possible on 400 vel cap, you'll just have to try it and see._

Any questions/comments will be answered.
Thanks.
